name: ROMANCE
description:
Photo taken in 2018 by a Canon 500D
 I am very much in love with this man, I don't remember having lived something like that before. I'm so afraid of this feeling that I end up directing it to myself with all the uncertainties of a future where I imagine us together, dating, kissing intertwined in endless conversations. You make me ridiculous, it's not funny and I no longer have clothes.
My Instagram: (@gabugusmão) (@gabunira)
